item.title: CVE-2021-24751|2024-08-03T19:42:16.566Z -- unknown -- generateblocks
item.description: The GenerateBlocks WordPress plugin before 1.4.0 does not validate the generateblocks/container block's tagName attribute, which could allow users with a role as low as contributor to perform Cross-Site Scripting attacks.
